<div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12" data-zesty-id="design:columns:1 column - 1 row my-3:76:98-1:1 column - 1 row:0">
<h6 style="text-align:center;" data-zesty-id="content:text:1:40">Athletic&nbsp;Programs</h6>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:2:2">
	Each year over 1,000 youth participate in The Salvation Army of Wake County&nbsp;Athletics Programs, learning the importance of team play and good sportsmanship. Always maintaining a Christ-centered atmosphere, there are pre-game devotions and prayers for each sport. Here, children are taught that winning means having fun, learning fundamental skills, and being a part of a team where they make&nbsp;a difference.&nbsp;For more information contact our Youth Programs at <a href="tel:919-832-6918" target="">919-832-6918</a>.
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:3:71"></div>
<p style="text-align:center;" class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-center" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:4:33"><a href="https://southernusa.salvationarmy.org/wake/athletic-programs#Free-Text-Area-1" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Nooners Adult Basketball</a><a href="https://southernusa.salvationarmy.org/wake/athletic-programs#Free-Text-Area-2" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Youth Basketball</a><a href="https://southernusa.salvationarmy.org/wake/athletic-programs#Free-Text-Area-3" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Baseball &amp; T-Ball</a><a href="https://southernusa.salvationarmy.org/wake/athletic-programs#Free-Text-Area-4" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Soccer&nbsp;</a><a href="https://southernusa.salvationarmy.org/wake/athletic-programs#Free-Text-Area-5" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Flag Football</a></p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:5:29"></div>
