<div class="rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-secondary-200 text-light" style="color:#FFFFFF;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:14:13"><h2>"Nooners" Adult Basketball</h2>

<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;">Often referred to as the "Nooners", adults will gather at The Salvation Army's Community Center to play pick-up games. There is no official league - just fun fellowship &amp; basketball.&nbsp;Please know that we will have to close the gym from time to time due to special events going on in the gym. We will try to give you advanced notice when those events occur.</span>
</p>

<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"></span>
</p>

<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Overview</strong></span>
</p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Registration is required</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">January 5&nbsp;- December 13, 2025</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Monday, Wednesday, and Friday 11:30 - 1:30 pm</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Guests are welcome for a one-time fee of $10.00</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Must be 18+ years of age</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">A Christ-centered atmosphere is maintained in our gym, so please act accordingly</span></li>
</ul>

<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Fees</strong></span>
</p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Option 1. Pay $10 each time you come</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Option 2.&nbsp;Pay $50 for a 12-visit pass (to be used only in 2025)</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Option 3.&nbsp;Pay $200 for a yearlong pass (good for all of 2025)</span></li>
</ul>

<p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-start"><a href="https://www.easyreg.org/cgi-bin/acct/UIVWDBCZX4/displayForm.pl?dir=9UZOCDC5_2023" target="_blank" class="btn btn-light gap-1 mt-2">Register</a></p></div>
<div class="py-5" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-xl:15:99"></div>
