<div class="rounded p-6 gap-3 bg-secondary-200 text-light" style="color:#FFFFFF;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:28:77"><h2>Baseball and T-Ball - 2026&nbsp;Registration Open now!</h2>

<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Overview</strong></span>
</p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Coach and player registration is required</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">March 16&nbsp;- May 22, 2026</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Ages 4 - 12&nbsp;years old (Based on age as of April 1, 2026)</span></li>
