	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Registration fee is $157 for all participants</span><ul>
		<li><span style="font-size:16px;">All payments should be made by credit card at the time of registration</span><span style="font-size:16px;"></span><span style="font-size:16px;"></span></li>
