<h5 data-zesty-id="content:text:30:40">Soccer</h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:31:37"><strong>Coaches, assistants, and players must register. The cost is $157&nbsp;per player.</strong></p>
<ul data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:32:66">
	<li>Coach registration is June 9, 2025</li>
	<li>Player registration&nbsp;is June 9,&nbsp;2025</li>
	<li>10-week program from August 4, 2025, through October 9, 2025&nbsp;</li>
	<li>All leagues are for boys and girls<ul>
		<li>4-year-old league</li>
		<li>5-6-year-old league</li>
		<li>7-8-year-old league</li>
		<li>9-11-year-old league</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Coaches, assistants, and players&nbsp;must register</li>
	<li>Mouth guards,&nbsp;shin guards, and molded&nbsp;cleats are required</li>
	<li>Practices are held on weekdays (determined by coach availability)<ul>
		<li>August 4&nbsp;- August 21, 2025 (5:00 or 6:00 p.m.)</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>Games start date:<ul>
		<li>August 25&nbsp;through October 9, 2025 (5:00 or 6:00 p.m.)</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>A Christ-centered atmosphere is maintained in our pre-game devotions and prayers for each&nbsp;sport.</li>
</ul>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:33:35"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:34:79">
	During registration there is an opportunity to make a donation to the Hurley Raynor Community Fund which helps provide scholarships to deserving youth and helps us maintain our facility. This fund honors Coach Hurley Raynor who has coached two generations of community center families.&nbsp;
</p>
<p class="cta-button-group d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-3 justify-content-start" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:35:39"><a href="https://www.easyreg.org/cgi-bin/acct/UIVWDBCZX4/displayForm.pl?dir=L1PUUZ4Q_2025" class="btn btn-info gap-1 mt-2">Coach Registration </a><a href="https://www.easyreg.org/cgi-bin/acct/UIVWDBCZX4/displayForm.pl?dir=ZLGJMSEP_2025" class="btn btn-secondary gap-1 mt-2">Player Registration</a></p>
